    %% Monitoring Integration
    Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>OpenShift Monitoring] -->|scrape metrics| CodeFlare

    %% Managed Resources
    CodeFlare -->|enhances security| RayCluster[Ray Clusters]

    %% Ray Cluster Dependencies
    RayCluster -->|managed by| KubeRay
